1
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,880
There is someone inside my body.

2
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:19,240
Get her out!

3
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:24,600
The all-night talk last night was quite fruitful.

4
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,200
But

5
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,120
it's a pity.

6
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,280
What's a pity?

7
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:30,320
You had a beautiful night and a lovely lady,

8
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:32,380
but you ended up studying Wentongzi.

9
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:35,000
I feel sorry for you.

10
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:38,800
What's wrong?

11
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:40,080
What do you smell?

12
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:42,400
Someone is getting really jealous.

13
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,640
Stop being glib.

14
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,800
It seems last night

15
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:51,200
someone else was awake all night too.

16
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,200
I just don't know

17
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:54,420
if it was for keeping watch or spying.

18
00:00:54,920 --> 00:00:55,450
Jianqin,

19
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,240
why don't you go back and rest?

20
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,040
I'd rather come out to investigate with you, Young Master,

21
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:00,320
than stay with Miss Tu

22
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,780
and listen to her scare me.

23
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,060
What are you doing?

24
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,440
We would like to ask

25
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,320
about Qu Dayou killing his mother.

26
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,240
Sir, what else do you remember?

27
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:15,720
Yes.

28
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,450
My son is the Plague Boy.

29
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,280
Of my perfectly good family,

30
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,850
I am the only one left alive.

31
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,800
What is the use of talking about this?

32
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,640
Just go back.

33
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:25,039
You can't help me.

34
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,039
Wait a minute.

35
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:29,340
Have you seen the Skeleton Grass on this?

36
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,600
Get out!

37
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,000
All of you, get out!

38
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,400
Young Master, are you alright?

39
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,200
I'm fine.

40
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,640
How can you be so barbaric?

41
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,800
What if you hurt my young master?

42
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,800
Old gentleman.

43
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:44,800
My Lord,

44
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:48,380
Something happened to the Madam of the Duke last night.

45
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,400
Director

46
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:24,720
Ji

47
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,720
How is my mother doing?

48
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,720
Your Highness.

49
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,290
The Madam of the Duke

50
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,440
is suffering from

51
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,920
an evil disease.

52
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,960
This, this is unprecedented.

53
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,360
Forgive

54
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,320
my ignorance.

55
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,240
I also have no clue at all.

56
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,160
Even if Hua Tuo were alive,

57
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,600
I'm afraid it would still be useless.

58
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,600
A bunch of losers.

59
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,720
What's the use of keeping you?

60
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,400
I might as well chop you up and feed you to the dogs.

61
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:16,200
Calm down, Your Highness.

62
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,240
Liu Chuan,

63
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,370
why are you here?

64
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,640
The virus has evolved to this extent.

65
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,840
Liu Chuan, what are you doing to my mother?

66
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,500
Emergency rescue, of course.

67
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,440
Can you save my mother?

68
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,640
Aren't you a coroner?

69
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,120
A coroner?

70
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,920
Doesn't a coroner just examine corpses?

71
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,360
I've never heard

72
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,490
that a coroner can also cure diseases.

73
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,720
Isn't this Young Master Liu?

74
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,560
You frequent brothels and casinos all year round.

75
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,360
When did you learn medicine?

76
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,800
You reek of alcohol and meat.

77
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:53,000
Don't choke the Duchess with the smell.

78
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,800
So you are the rumored

79
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,160
Young Master Liu.

80
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,720
I've heard so much about you.

81
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,800
In my opinion,

82
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,720
your diagnostic skills

83
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,600
are quite extraordinary.

84
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,720
You look at money,

85
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,240
smell alcohol,

86
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,700
ask about gambling debts,

87
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,180
and feel your reputation.

88
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,400
Someone who deals with the dead every day.

89
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,120
If you fail to cure the Duchess,

90
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,720
how can you take the responsibility?

91
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,649
Are you doctors?

92
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:19,760
If you can't cure her,

93
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:20,720
get out of the way.

94
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,320
You... How dare you insult us?

95
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,160
How vulgar.

96
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,000
Your Highness,

97
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,200
if you really let him treat the Duchess,

98
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,320
and something goes wrong,

99
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,640
I'm afraid we won't be able to help.

100
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,920
Preposterous.

101
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,600
Your hands touch dead bodies every day,

102
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,920
and you dare to save the Duchess?

103
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,400
Aren't you afraid of killing her?

104
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,600
What are your intentions?

105
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,920
Then tell me what to do.

106
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,920
All of you, shut up.

107
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,280
Liu Chuan,

108
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,060
can you really save my mother?

109
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,200
Right now,

110
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,240
I can't guarantee a complete cure.

111
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,770
I can only temporarily relieve the symptoms.

112
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,600
There's no better way right now.

113
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,040
You saw your uncle.

114
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,700
What was the result in the end?

115
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,400
This...

116
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,640
Liu Chuan,

117
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,680
if you can cure my mother,

118
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,240
I will give you whatever you want.

119
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,480
But if you can't,

120
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,920
I'll have your head.

121
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,240
Glad I made it in time.

122
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,840
I thought it was some miracle cure,

123
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,700
but it's just anesthetic powder.

124
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,260
What are you doing with the knife?

125
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,240
You...

126
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,520
Are not going to...

127
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,050
Exactly.

128
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,400
I need to make an incision and drain the blood.

129
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,360
Nonsense!

130
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,360
This is simply child's play.

131
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:19,320
Your Highness,

132
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:21,080
if you really let him treat the Duchess,

133
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,720
I fear she will die at his hands.

134
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,320
Yes.

135
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,240
The virus has already invaded the body through the bloodstream.

136
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,360
The only way is to make an incision, drain the blood, and remove the rotting flesh.

137
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,600
Although there are certain risks,

138
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,530
I will do my best.

139
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,450
Don't worry.

140
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,320
Stop!

141
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,740
Your Highness,

142
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,520
you absolutely must not let him mess around.

143
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,520
If we don't stop him,

144
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,960
the Duchess will die by his hands.

145
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:38,600
Your Highness.

146
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,640
You two, shut up.

147
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,530
If you can treat her, do it. If not, get out.

148
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,320
Mother.

149
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,320
Mother, wake up.

150
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,440
Mother.

151
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,920
Mother.

152
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,840
Why isn't my mother responding?

153
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,780
She is dead.

154
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,880
Dead, dead, dead.

155
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,520
Dead.

156
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,920
The Duchess is dead.

157
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,320
Shut up!

158
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,640
Mother!

159
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:40,920
The...

160
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,800
The Duchess.

161
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,040
Guards!

162
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:46,520
Drag these gossips out

163
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,920
and beat them to death.

164
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,400
We are innocent!

165
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,970
Princess, we are innocent!

166
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,440
Injustice.

167
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,680
Liu Chuan.

168
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,120
You saved my mother.

169
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,080
I will give you whatever you want.

170
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:00,720
Even if...

171
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,800
Even if you want this mansion,

172
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,000
I wouldn't hesitate.

173
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,400
Even...

174
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:05,720
even if you want...

175
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,200
If you really want to save your mother,

176
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,720
we must find the murderer

177
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,660
and trace the source of the virus.

178
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,130
I still need your cooperation.

179
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,840
How many times have I told you

180
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,240
not to pat me from behind?

181
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,520
The sound seems to come from inside.

182
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,360
I found similar powder on

183
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,580
the Princess's uncle's body before.

184
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,180
As expected, the Plague Boy is man-made.

185
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,620
This is the Princess's uncle,

186
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,400
the Princess,

187
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,520
the Duchess of Jiaguo,

188
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,120
and the workers.

189
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,560
Oh no.

190
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,360
Why does the watchman's drum today

191
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,560
seem half a quarter earlier than usual?

192
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,040
Water.

193
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:16,600
Stop.

194
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,280
He's the one

195
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,560
who killed my uncle

196
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,090
and wants to kill my mother.

197
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,450
Qu Dayou is still alive.

198
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,680
The reason he became a Plague Boy

199
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:27,880
was also man-made.

200
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:28,520
Right?

201
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:30,560
The debt the Medicine God Society owes my family

202
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,520
should be paid.

203
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,200
Watch out.
